{"tid":532162,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)生死時速 魔間行者 無名殺機","createTime":"2018-01-17T14:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T19:07:54.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2de51f075e953219a09a91f06d5cda1b5ba420e2","tid":532162,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=db3770d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4d083d4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c5/Speedposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc5%2FSpeedposter.jpg&h=5581070f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/2b/Constantine_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F2b%2FConstantine_poster.jpg&h=b9bfeb01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/33/Unknown_2011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F33%2FUnknown_2011.jpg&h=6a8b660d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.劇情內容敘述一名退休警員霍華&middot;潘恩（Howard Payne，丹尼斯&middot;霍普飾演），花了多年時間計畫出天衣無縫的計畫打算搶錢，後來在計畫當中，潘恩打算利用困在電梯的人質達成目的，但是被洛杉磯警察局特殊武器戰術小組警員傑克&middot;崔文（Jack Traven，基努&middot;李維飾演）破壞了其計畫，成功救出了人質並且讓潘恩無法達成目的。<br />\n<br />\n2.故事從墨西哥開始，一個年輕人曼奴爾在一個廢墟中找到了一把包裹在納粹旗幟裏的「命運之矛」，他一抓住這矛就好像著了魔，向洛杉磯去了。行進間如同瘟疫般為周遭的一切生物帶來死亡。「命運之矛」乃基督教的聖物，在第二次世界大戰後此矛下落不明，這昔日用來刺死耶穌、染有耶穌血液的矛，誰若得到它便能掌握世界..<br />\n<br />\n3.馬丁&middot;哈里斯與他的妻子麗茲蒞臨柏林參加一個生物技術研討會，夫妻倆到達酒店入住房間時，馬丁突然發現他最重要的公事包忘在機場，便丟下麗茲搭一輛計程車回去取。但計程車行進途中發生車禍，整輛車落入橋河中，馬丁頭部遭受撞擊後陷入昏迷，車上的女司機吉娜將馬丁救上岸後，因為身為波士尼亞非法移民而只好迅速離開現場。馬丁被送醫後昏迷四天，清醒後因為頭部撞擊而出現失憶狀態..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3ee63dd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=88df4764\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d869560e772d3ec87589a361cc2a19991a6fe4c8","tid":532162,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e15f2bcdd14b6263c4aa768b4c487c12d74a62","tid":532162,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"